EXT. DAY: POLICE CAR - DOWNTOWN MANSFIELD, OHIO 2
Daniels sits in the back of a police car in a checked suit. 
He looks out at the rest of the security cars in his parade, 
then at the swarm of onlookers.
The sidewalks are filled with them: many swear at his car, 
some gesture violently, others just try to peek in. Daniels 
cracks a wry smile, head pressed to the window.

